हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: "Imperial Concubine Cultivation Manual for Students with Excellent Grades" is a short Chinese drama series that blends historical fantasy with modern romance, following a brilliant modern-day student who unexpectedly time-travels to an imperial era. Armed with her intelligence and sharp wit, she navigates palace politics, rivalries, and romance as she rises through the ranks to become a powerful imperial concubine. Using her academic skills in unexpected ways, she outsmarts scheming courtiers and wins the emperor's favor, all while adapting to a world far removed from her own. The series combines humor, drama, and light-hearted intrigue, making it a popular pick among fans of historical time-travel dramas.
